    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="kicker">The process</span>
        <h1 class="mt14">Diagnosis → alignment → expression (and sustainable growth).</h1>
        <p class="lead mt14">
          This isn’t a content audit. It’s a clarity diagnosis — then a brand voice alignment — then content created through a coherent lens.
        </p>

        <div class="grid-2 mt24">
          <div class="card">
            <h2>1. Diagnose — Brand & business analysis</h2>
            <p class="small">
              We begin with a deep analysis of your business to uncover where clarity is missing, what’s blocking trust, and why current content isn’t converting.
              Think symptoms → root cause.
            </p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Messaging & positioning diagnosis</li>
              <li>Guest journey + booking friction</li>
              <li>What your content says vs what you really offer</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2>2. Align — Brand voice & DNA</h2>
            <p class="small">
              Together, we define your brand DNA: how it sounds, how it feels, what it stands for, and who it’s truly for.
              This becomes the foundation for everything you communicate.
            </p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Voice pillars (tone, rhythm, language)</li>
              <li>Values and boundaries (what you’re not)</li>
              <li>A clear “who it’s for” filter</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-2 mt14">
          <div class="card">
            <h2>3. Express — Content & storytelling</h2>
            <p class="small">
              Only once clarity is established do we create. Every asset is expressed through your clarified voice so it feels coherent and human.
            </p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Retreat films and brand stories</li>
              <li>Website visuals and messaging</li>
              <li>Social content that doesn’t feel forced</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2>4. Sustain — Ongoing partnership (optional)</h2>
            <p class="small">
              For brands ready to grow consciously: long-term support as your story evolves. This turns short-term content into long-term growth.
            </p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Strategic guidance & planning</li>
              <li>Messaging refinement over time</li>
              <li>Support as your offerings evolve</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card mt24">
          <h2>What you’ll walk away with</h2>
          <div class="grid-3 mt14">
            <div class="card soft">
              <h3>Clarity</h3>
              <p class="small m0">A brand voice you can actually use (and repeat) across your team.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card soft">
              <h3>Confidence</h3>
              <p class="small m0">Messaging that matches the experience — so the right guests self-select.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card soft">
              <h3>Conversion</h3>
              <p class="small m0">More direct inquiries and bookings because trust is built before arrival.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

